DataElement.preferredName: One Repetition Maximum Calculated Weight Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: The numeric response that represents the calculated maximum amount of force that can be generated in one maximal muscle contraction or the maximum amount of weight that can be cycled through one repetition of a particular movement or exercise measured in pounds.
